column1: Demographic Trends of People Receiving COVID-19 Vaccinations in the United States
Date generated: Tue Apr 27 2021 08:33:10 GMT-0400 (Eastern Daylight Time)

Due to a data synchronization error between April 3-5 2021 the daily count of doses reporting “Unknown Age” in the COVID-19 Case Surveillance Public Use Data incorrectly appeared higher than expected. The issue was resolved on April 6 2021 and the count of doses reporting ‘Unknown Age’ accurately reflects the totals reported to CDC.
